reviewText: my kids love veggie tales and this set was perfect for my oldest who has been wanting to see the cucmber hero he has been seeing on veggie tale movies

My daughter loves this dvd.  Contains all 3 Larryboy movies and all the Larryboy cartoons.  While not as good as the regular Veggietales, the cartoons are not that bad.  However, just note the cartoons are just regular cartoons and not computer generated.

My kids loves Veggie Tales and this fit right in with the collection they already have. This DVD has valuable life lessons in a way that kids can understand and it teaches them about God in a way that is fun for them. Would recommend to anyone one looking for a good morals box set for there kids
